WEBVTT

00:02:58.702 --> 00:03:01.576
for not jumping at the opportunity of going

00:03:01.576 --> 00:03:03.595
to the middle of the city in the middle

00:03:03.595 --> 00:03:06.944
of a working day to attend, physically,

00:03:06.944 --> 00:03:10.364
a public hearing that has no impact

00:03:10.364 --> 00:03:12.304
whatsoever?

00:03:12.304 --> 00:03:16.692
Conflict is bound to happen between a system

00:03:16.692 --> 00:03:22.887
that no longer represents, nor has any dialogue capacity,

00:03:22.887 --> 00:03:25.965
and citizens that are increasingly used

00:03:25.965 --> 00:03:28.311
to representing themselves.

00:03:28.311 --> 00:03:30.615
